{"id":846984,"date":[{"year":1991,"month":9,"day":10}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会·为读者服务","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"105","ytitle":"","mtitle":"给你","ftitle":"","authors":["向北"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一次相遇的结局是别离"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一次别离都始自相遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云只开一个晴日，虹只驾一个黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪只落一个冬季，为你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当春季来临，所有的雪都殉情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那就摘一张阔些的树叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包一片湖光回去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回去夹在诗集里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扁扁的，像压过的相思"}]}